### ===== Dispatch Sheets =====
### Get all Dispatch Sheets
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets
Accept: application/json

### Get Dispatch Sheet by ID
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new Dispatch Sheet
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "LKW-1"
}

### Update Dispatch Sheet
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "LKW Groß"
}

### Delete Dispatch Sheet
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/3
Accept: application/json

### Get DispatchSheets articles
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/units

### Set Required Units for Dispatch Sheet
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/required-units
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Accept: application/json

{
  "unitId": 6338,
  "count": 50
}

### Get Required Units for Dispatch Sheet
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/required-units
Accept: application/json

### Update Required Units (different unit)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/required-units
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Accept: application/json

{
  "unitId": 2,
  "count": 30
}

### Delete Required Unit (set count to 0)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/required-units
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Accept: application/json

{
  "unitId": 1,
  "count": 0
}

### Delete Required Unit (using DELETE endpoint)
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/DispatchSheets/1/required-units/2
Accept: application/json
